attributes.description:
Background; Ph.d in Philosophy & DIY filmmaker. 


After BA, MA and a Ph.d in Philosophy I left the spheres of academia and migrated to the get my hands dirty with hardcore entrepreneurship and start-up collaboration in a big corporate.

Best Alfred

attributes.label: Pedro Parraguez
attributes.description:
I’m the co-founder and CEO of Dataverz, a technology-based startup where we develop decision-support systems to tackle complex societal challenges. I’m fascinated by the power of human imagination, self-organised large-scale collaborations, and the intricacies of the design process.

Before this adventure, I was a postdoctoral researcher at the Engineering Systems Division in DTU Management Engineering, the Deputy Director of Innovation and Entrepreneurship for the School of Management of the Pontificia Universidad Católica de Chile, run another start-up, did some consultancy, have been university lecturer, and worked in a few other jobs related with science and technology.
attributes.title: Pedro Parraguez
